editorialSummary.text: Corner deli featuring a menu of breakfast items, sandwiches & salads, plus coffee drinks.

originalText.text: great back up deli when my other delis a little closer to my house don't have a cook. love the chop cheese here. would def get anything else and even for delivery- they got great tacos and usually if you're a local they'll deliver beer too. very well made sandwiches here though

originalText.text: The guy that works in the deli in the morning is super nice!!! the older man that works the front in the morning is very nice as well. Today was a different story. I’m a regular customer, I’m in there mon-fri spending my hard earned money. When the older man isn’t there they put a younger one there to do the job and I’m sorry he is rude and can’t make coffee right at all and gets angry when you inform him. I have to ask him what he did to the coffee that it taste so bitter? This morning he got upset because I brought my coffee back asking for sugar. If you don’t like your job find another one!!!! A lot of ppl I know from the area says he is always rude like that always. When you spending your money you shouldn’t have to deal with horrible customer service. I wonder who owns this store!!!!

originalText.text: Food was good and very fair pricing for the city. Local deli and tasted fresh.  Lots of drinks to chose from and chips if you want them.  Downside was they didn't have the corn beef or pastrami on the menu, which is why I went here.  So I'm not sure how much of a selection they really have for a.deli.

originalText.text: DO NOT ORDER FROM HERE!!! The minimum you have to wait is 45 minutes to get your order, then they almost never pick up the phone and the dude that does pick up doesn’t speak English and acts like your the one that isint speaking clearly. They only know sandwich names, brands of drinks/snacks and can’t speak a full sentence in English, my chopped cheese came cold and when I opened up my Pepsi it blasted out on my floor because I think they told the delivery guy to shake it before they give it to me! This place is horrible and if you do plan on getting food from here GO IN PERSON. Oh and by the way whatever you do when you order don’t say things unrelated to the order or else they flip out and threaten to call the cops!!

originalText.text: Worse customer service! I called at 8:16 am to place an order for egg whites, I got there at 8:40 am order wasn't ready and when I got to my job my order was incomplete! I was so frustrated I called and the guy started saying not to eat just bring it if you want that make me so mad I went back and got my money back. He disrespect me so much that I wouldn't recommend  nobody to go there because of his attitude. Also that happened 2 weeks prior but when I got to the deli my order was never made.
